    <long-description>
      (Hind-E) Entered production in 1976. Manufactured 1976-1986. It was the most widely produced version with more than 1,500 made.
      Armed with the more advanced 9M114 Shturm-V (AT-6 Spiral). Four of these missiles are mounted on four outer wing pylons.
      In 1986 it was modernised to carry 16 9M114 Shturm-V (AT-6 Spiral) missiles.Also armed with 12.7 mm turret,
      B8V20 unguided missile launchers (20 S-8 rockets), B13L1 unguided missile launchers (S-13 rockets), heavy rockets S-24B.
      Engines TV3-117V
    </long-description>

